6.title: Who Do You Love?

episode of.title: La Story: The New Class (TV Series 2016– )

6.plot: Tensions are still high between Juliet and Taylor, and Julia's not pleased that someone is talking behind her back. Meanwhile, the boy's meet up before Luke's DJ gig to discuss their own drama. Luke's confused about Maddie, but everyone else is confused about what's going on with Shae and his love life.

episode of.title: La Story: The New Class (TV Series 2016– )

7.plot: Luke's DJing at the SLS Hotel and everyone's invited. Julia hears that someone's talking smack...again. This time, will she go down without a fight? Later, Luke and Maddie finally have THE conversation.

episode of.title: La Story: The New Class (TV Series 2016– )

episode of.title: La Story: The New Class (TV Series 2016– )

11.plot: Kaylyn and Taylor devise a plan for specific teams for golf and Maddie isn't happy. Meanwhile, Julia denies her history with Luke, but Trent isn't buying it. Finally, Maddie confronts Luke and this time his story may be changing.

episode of.title: La Story: The New Class (TV Series 2016– )

12.plot: Tensions are running high in palm springs with Maddie and Luke while the rest of the group tries to make the best of their trip. Taylor convinces Luke to have a conversation with Maddie to finally put the rumors to rest. Will Maddie finally get the closure she's after?
